CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 22, 1967, pg. 13 reads: "Alpha Hymn - Members of Omicron Chapter of Alpha Phi Alpha Fraternity joined Charles Highgate in singing the beautiful "Alpha Hymn" during intermission of their recent dance in ballroom of the Pick-Roosevelt Hotel."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Phi Alpha members encircling Charles Highgate, singing the "Alpha Hymn" during intermission at dance held in the Pick-Roosevelt ballroom
